snippet.title: Solitomb - new solitaire/poker/dungeon-crawling roguelike, now available!
snippet.description:
This is a quick announcement of my new PICO-8 game, Solitomb, now available on: https://krajzeg.itch.io/solitomb

🃏Stack cards 
😈 Form combos 
⚔️ Fight monsters 
🏹 Gain abilities 
🤗 Emerge victorious

Solitomb is a free-to-play, pay-what-you-want PICO-8 title that you can play in any browser of your choice.
